text: @FedExHelp so i live in a college dorm, and the only mail we have is a parcel center which closed. explain to me why you would drop it at that front door of a populated area and not give me a follow up email that it was delivered

@LEVIIA7HAN Hello Howard, my name is Karin. I apologize for the inconvenience this has caused and this is not the experience we want to provide. I would be happy to look into this matter, please DM the tracking number, delivery address and contact information. Thank you!
